<p><strong>Highlights:</strong></p>
<ul>
  <li>This research conducts a spatial–temporal analysis of real-time navigation data.</li>
  <li>This research reveals four typical traffic accessibility evolution patterns.</li>
  <li>A new indicator is introduced to resemble the spin direction in the Ising model.</li>
  <li>Phase transition-like phenomena are identified through the phase diagrams.</li>
</ul>

